{{Infobox football biography | name = Celestino | image = | fullname = Celestino Marques Silva Ilnhasse | birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1988|05|28}} | birth_place = [[Bissau]], [[Guinea-Bissau]] | height = {{convert|1.66|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}} | position = Striker | currentclub = [[Alcanenense]] | clubnumber = | years1 =2007 | clubs1 =[[FC Farul Constanța|Farul Constanța]] | caps1 = | goals1 = | years2 =2013– | clubs2 =[[Alcanenense]] | caps2 = 3 | goals2 =1 | pcupdate = {{date|2016-02-16}} | nationalyears1 = | nationalteam1 = | nationalcaps1 = | nationalgoals1 = }}
'''Celestino Marques Silva Ilnhasse''' (born 20 May 1988) is a football [[midfielder]] from [[Guinea-Bissau]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cugetliber.ro/1184792400/articol/1135/celestino-marques-a-impresionat-la-farul-ii/|title=Celestino Marques a impresionat la Farul II|last=Bocai|first=Marian|date=19 July 2007|work=[[List of newspapers in Romania|Ziarul Cuget Liber Constanta]]|language=Romanian|accessdate=30 October 2010}}</ref> who plays for [[Alcanenense]].
