'''Elson Quincy Hooi''' (born 1 October 1991) is a [[Curaçao]]an footballer who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|right winger]] for [[Eredivisie]]-side [[ADO Den Haag]].<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/elson-hooi/ | title = Elson Hooi | publisher = worldfootball.net | accessdate = 12 November 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://eredivisielive.nl/eredivisie/speler/1064273/elson-hooi/ |title=Elson Hooi |publisher=eredivisielive.nl |accessdate=11 August 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120922140111/http://eredivisielive.nl/eredivisie/speler/1064273/elson-hooi/ |archivedate=22 September 2012 |df=dmy }}</ref><ref>[http://tb01.tipsbladet.dk/nyhed/superliga/avis-vendsyssel-ff-lejer-i-fc-twente Avis: Vendsyssel FF lejer i FC Twente]‚tipsbladet.dk, 12 June 2017</ref> He formerly played for [[NAC Breda]], [[Viborg FF]], [[FC Volendam]], [[Ermis Aradippou FC|Ermis Aradippou]], and [[Vendsyssel FF]].
==Career== He was raised in the Netherlands, but was born in Curaçao and represents the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]].<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.national-football-teams.com/player/59414/Elson_Hooi.html | title=Hooi, Elson | publisher=National Football Teams | accessdate=15 October 2018 }}</ref> He won the 2017 Caribbean Cup with the Curaçao national team, and was also the top scorer of that competition.
