{{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Estadio Los Cuchumatanes | nick_name = | image = | location = {{flagicon|Guatemala}} [[Huehuetenango]], [[Guatemala]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | opened = January 17, 2007 | renovated = 2007 | expanded = | closed = | demolished = | owner = Municipalidad de Huehuetenango | operator = | surface = Grass | Constructor = | construction_cost = [[Guatemalan_quetzal|Q]] 26,000,000 <ref>Source: http://www.prensalibre.com/pl/2007/enero/21/161367.html</ref> | architect = | former_names = | nicknames = | tenants = [[Deportivo Xinabajul]] | seating_capacity = 5,340 | dimensions = }}
'''Estadio Los Cuchumatanes''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadium]] located in [[Huehuetenango]], [[Guatemala]]. It is home to [[football (soccer)|football]] club [[Deportivo Xinabajul]]. Its capacity is around 5,340.<ref>Source: http://www.prensalibre.com.gt/pl/2007/enero/20/161327.html</ref> The stadium opened its doors on January 17, 2007.
