'''Kuan Tai''' ([[Traditional Chinese]]: 關帝文化) is a [[Macau]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club, which plays in [[Macao]]. The team have been withdrwan from the Macau's first division, the [[Campeonato da 1ª Divisão do Futebol]] in 2014.


