{{Spanish name|Castillo|Galindo}}

'''Rut Castillo Galindo''' (born 16 September 1990) is a Mexican individual [[rhythmic gymnast]]. She represents her nation at international competitions. She competed at world championships, including at the 2009, 2011 and [[2015 World Rhythmic Gymnastics Championships]].<ref>{{cite web |title=34th RHYTHMIC GYMNASTICS WORLD CHAMPIONSHIPS in Stuttgart (GER) - Entry List by NOC |quote=CASTILLO GALINDO Rut |url=http://gym.longinestiming.com/File/00000E0101FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF02 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507225735/http://gym.longinestiming.com/File/00000E0101FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF02 |archive-date=7 May 2016 |publisher=LonginesTiming.com |date=6 September 2015 |accessdate=27 January 2016}}</ref>

Since February 2016, Rut Castillo is the image of the Process Improvement departament in [[Beecker Consulting]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.beeckerconsulting.com/patrocinio.php|title=Beecker Consulting|accessdate=25 February 2016|website=www.beeckerconsulting.com}}</ref>

